to a much better therapist.

153
00:07:43,230 --> 00:07:45,799
Pay $2.99 to accept.

154
00:07:47,935 --> 00:07:49,336
Hoo boy.

155
00:07:49,436 --> 00:07:51,405
Mr. Simpson,
when you found out

156
00:07:51,471 --> 00:07:55,876
your mother was alive,
were you conflicted?

157
00:07:58,078 --> 00:08:01,048
I decided it was time
my father and I had a talk

158
00:08:01,181 --> 00:08:03,650
about what really happened
to my mother.

159
00:08:05,385 --> 00:08:07,554
