- She is.

160
00:08:07,621 --> 00:08:08,889
Why wasn't there a funeral?

161
00:08:08,956 --> 00:08:10,157
There was too much going on.

162
00:08:10,224 --> 00:08:11,758
My wife just died,
for God's sake.

163
00:08:11,859 --> 00:08:14,928
