not telling me about Mom.

164
00:08:14,995 --> 00:08:17,164
Well, son,
when a man and a woman

165
00:08:17,231 --> 00:08:18,498
love each other very much,

166
00:08:18,565 --> 00:08:20,968
they want to make a baby
that is immediately

167
