When she said "outta sight,"
she wasn't kidding around.

174
00:08:36,016 --> 00:08:38,018
- Why did you lie?
- To protect you.

175
00:08:38,118 --> 00:08:39,586
Protect me from what?

176
00:08:39,653 --> 00:08:40,954
To protect you from a woman

177
00:08:41,021 --> 00:08:43,156
who didn't love me enough!

178
00:08:43,223 --> 00:08:45,392
Oh, my God,
I wasn't protecting you,

179
00:08:45,492 --> 00:08:46,492
I was protecting me.

180
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:48,495
From the shame
of a wife who left.

181
00:08:48,562 --> 00:08:51,665
Because I never gave her
what she wanted most,

182
00:08:51,765 --> 00:08:53,333
which was to leave me.

183
