You and I have each other
and that's all we'll ever need.

188
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,822
This isn't over.

189
00:09:15,889 --> 00:09:17,024
What did you just think?

190
00:09:17,090 --> 00:09:18,525
You heard me!

191
00:09:18,592 --> 00:09:20,060
That must have been difficult.

192
00:09:20,194 --> 00:09:21,895
How did you deal
with your grief?

193
00:09:21,962 --> 00:09:23,430
I tried everything.

194
00:09:23,497 --> 00:09:25,465
