angry, messed-up young men.

198
00:09:31,405 --> 00:09:32,606
No, thank you!

199
00:09:32,706 --> 00:09:34,007
I went to the church.

200
00:09:34,074 --> 00:09:35,075
It didn't help.

201
00:09:35,175 --> 00:09:36,243
I lost my mother

202
00:09:36,276 --> 00:09:38,178
and I can't get rid of the pain.

203
00:09:38,212 --> 00:09:41,048
Have you considered
another religion? Hmm?

204
00:09:41,114 --> 00:09:43,951
Then one night,
I came to a decision.

205
00:09:44,051 --> 00:09:45,853
Why did she go to Utah?

206
00:09:45,886 --> 00:09:49,790
