birthday.

218
00:10:24,725 --> 00:10:28,729
Please, Dad. I need to know
what happened to her.

219
00:10:28,795 --> 00:10:31,298
Oh, I can't say no
to that face.

220
00:10:31,431 --> 00:10:34,635
