399
00:19:10,584 --> 00:19:11,685
But I can't stay.

400
00:19:12,452 --> 00:19:16,256
Just know
I'm always with you in here.

401
00:19:17,357 --> 00:19:19,893
I guess that'll have to do.

402
00:19:21,195 --> 00:19:23,997
I even miss you sometimes.

403
00:19:24,064 --> 00:19:26,633
Wait! Doctor! Let's talk!

404
00:19:26,733 --> 00:19:27,801
Was it a dream?

405
00:19:27,868 --> 00:19:31,038
There's no way I'll ever know.

406
00:19:31,138 --> 00:19:33,273
It wasn't a dream.
I was there.

407
00:19:33,373 --> 00:19:37,744
There's no reliable way
I'll ever know.

408
00:19:37,878 --> 00:19:40,280
Either way, Dad, it's wonderful.

